thread.title: Monica Len

author: Monica Len
title: Monica Len
text:
At first glance it seems like Strawberry Net has everything. But, disappointingly, the range of make-up products (particularly) is limited. Many brands have only 1 or 2 items and it takes some searching to find what you are looking for.
Website layout needs an overhaul but the checkout process is seamless.
Love the discounts (and realise that the above issue is related to this somehow) and will keep coming back.
